oh and also eCPS 💊🧬🦠 I loveeeeee the material provided by our college so much because it is very well organized and easy to refer back to!!! 

I know it can get overwhelming with all this different types of study material available and so here is what I do. I decide on one chapter of pharmacology, study that from the book first in detail, then refer it through the college’s material and then make my own notes on it and that way I revise it multiple times and also cover all the information needed for that topic 🫶🏻📚💊
